    <baseline year="2018">
     <comment>
      <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. Outdated National Disaster Risk Management Framework 
2. Disaster Risk Management  Capacities at sub-national level is weak
3. Opportunities exists for Disaster Risk Management integration at different levels
